ore":0,"quote":{"pid":"afaf247224e7cce06ba0df210b5fad4421fee2c9","tid":2266320,"uid":161417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"行運超人屌打全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"要係同行運星合體嘅最終型態"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"諗起舊登post: 孫悟空、行運超人同叮噹邊個好打啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"仲要加埋黃金體驗鎮魂曲"},{"pid":"29ad6327dbf2dd03b18aaafed93de49dc6d36c8e","tid":2266320,"uid":28792,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆<br />\n天元突破紅蓮裸眼打反螺旋族部機都係險勝<br />\n琦玉打乜都一拳秒 仲要能力睇唔到極限<br />\n我個人就買老師喇<br />\n畢竟搞笑漫畫角色接近無敵"},{"pid":"5e44a81597f45ff97dedddc924f0f3695a0339c5","tid":2266320,"uid":214367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"全王"},{"pid":"0be583b0cbd12257528e652b5d8698c6ea143b73","tid":2266320,"uid":144275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"老師淨係龍珠個班都未打得贏啦<br />\n老師認真一拳都係地球表面打度痕出黎<br />\n龜仙人N年前已經可以打爆月亮<br />\nN年後既超藍悟空勁龜仙人幾多倍?"},{"pid":"ba505c281825290d48d9311e495c63ffbbb7f2f3","tid":2266320,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲比較冇意義<br />\n唔係同一步作品點比較<br />\n同埋勝負可以俾好多因素影響<br />\n例如埼玉同夜神月面對面打琦玉贏硬<br />\n但係如果一個喺北極一個喺南極<br />\n咁就係夜神月贏<br />\n所以冇得比較<br />\n打和"},{"pid":"93d6b44dd8d22c9a8cf2f111a0e1f3b18688f9a7","tid":2266320,"uid":256957,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ok, I took some pixel measurements of the gigadrill as compared to the size of the observable universe. With the OU being 46.6 billion light years in diameter, this gives us a GD with a height of 2.73E27 meters and a radius of 9.71E26 meters. It's not a perfect cone, but it's damn close, so I'm just going to use the cone volume formula of V=pi r^2 h/3. Or V= pi * 9.71E26 * 9.71E26 * 2.73E27 / 3. Which gives us an overall volume of 2.7E81 cubic meters...almost exactly one OOM above our previous estimate. Applying the density of diamond again, we end up with 9.47E84 kg.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gurennlagann/images/8/88/Super_Tengen_Toppa_Size.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fgurennlagann%2Fimages%2F8%2F88%2FSuper_Tengen_Toppa_Size.jpg&h=c5050b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n假設一拳嘅威力可以打得爆一個可觀察宇宙範圍<br />\n要打夠<span class=\"red\">7</span>次先可以完全打爆個超天元鑽頭<br />\n而假設一拳只可以打爆一個可觀察宇宙所有能量質量<br />\n要打夠<span class=\"red\">5.0e70</span>次(5後面即係有69個零)先可以打爆個超天元鑽頭"},{"pid":"416fa1b93f1875add9a2f279af44b6f5e45c7a64","tid":2266320,"uid":102716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f01fd2a0912d30e5d5674a8e22d265aa6b04aa1","tid":2266320,"uid":55552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5bfc9b88931a6eabc45f7e6ff49ba7f70de4e1c0","tid":2266320,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"唔多漫畫點比較<br />\n<br />\n設定上<br />\n崎玉乜都係一拳搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"設你老母，波蘿斯都唔知打咗幾拳啦"},{"pid":"394ddf227e5076cf8e988c5f820969e205b5480c","tid":2266320,"uid":69235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"我忘記了，今天是超巿的特賣日啊！！<br />\n<br />\n然後一拳搞掂"},{"pid":"bb79cb9a9c3612b4b4fe2ca2269f76d34f9996e9","tid":2266320,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"天元突破 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無撚敵"}]}